OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FFailing NHS hospitals in England will
OL,7,Fbe named and shamed in league tables
OL,8,Fand managers sacked if they cannot
OL,9,Fimprove patient care and take control
OL,10,Fof finances, the Health Secretary is
OL,11,Fexpected to say on Wednesday.
OL,13,FDuring the NHS Providers conference in
OL,14,FLiverpool, Wes Streeting will tell
OL,15,Fleaders there "will be no more rewards
OL,16,Ffor failure" as he sets out a package
OL,17,Fof measures aimed at tackling poor
OL,18,Fperformance.
