OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FStreeting will say: "Today we are
OL,7,Fannouncing the reforms to make sure
OL,8,Fevery penny of extra investment is
OL,9,Fwell spent and cuts waiting times for
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,F"There'll be no more turning a blind
OL,13,Feye to failure. We will drive the
OL,14,Fhealth service to improve, so patients
OL,15,Fget more out of it for what taxpayers
OL,16,Fput in."
