OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FNHS leaders have expressed concerns
OL,7,Fthat the move could demoralise staff
OL,8,Fwith Nuffield Trust's chief executive,
OL,9,FThea Stein, accusing ministers of
OL,10,F"falling for the appealing notion of a
OL,11,Fmagic productivity tree which will
OL,12,Fmake the NHS more efficient just by
OL,13,Fshaking the magic tree harder."
OL,15,FStein said: "We know from the special
OL,16,Fmeasures for quality regime that
OL,17,Fnaming and shaming NHS trusts can make
OL,18,Fit harder to recruit staff, which
OL,19,Fdoesn't help patient care at all.
