OL,6,FNHS chief executive Amanda Pritchard
OL,7,Fsaid: "While NHS leaders welcome
OL,8,Faccountability, it is critical that
OL,9,Fresponsibility comes with the
OL,10,Fnecessary support and development.
OL,12,F"The extensive package of reforms,
OL,13,Fdeveloped together with government,
OL,14,Fwill empower all leaders working in
OL,15,Fthe NHS and it will give them the
OL,16,Ftools they need to provide the best
OL,17,Fpossible services for our patients."
