OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FPoorly performing hospitals will be
OL,7,Fshamed meanwhile, the best NHS
OL,8,Fperformers will be given more control
OL,9,Fover spending to help modernise their
OL,10,Fbuildings, equipment and technology.
OL,12,FThe Department of Health argues this
OL,13,Fwill benefit top-performing trusts as
OL,14,Funder the current system there is
OL,15,Flittle incentive for trusts to run
OL,16,Fbudget surpluses as they are unable to
OL,17,Fbenefit from them.
