OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FThe health secretary is expected to
OL,7,Fargue: "The Budget showed this
OL,8,FGovernment prioritises the NHS,
OL,9,Fproviding the investment needed to
OL,10,Frebuild the health service" said
OL,11,FStreeting.
OL,13,F"Our health service must attract top
OL,14,Ftalent, be far more transparent to the
OL,15,Fpublic who pay for it, and run as
OL,16,Fefficiently as global businesses.
OL,18,F"With the combination of investment
OL,19,Fand reform, we will turn the NHS
OL,20,Faround and cut waiting times from 18
OL,21,Fmonths to 18 weeks."
