OL,7,Fmanagers will be published before
OL,8,FApril next year, with those who do
OL,9,Fwell given financial rewards.
OL,11,FThe deputy chief executive of NHS
OL,12,FProviders, Saffron Cordery, said the
OL,13,Fscale of the challenge facing NHS
OL,14,Fleaders was "huge" and they were
OL,15,F"pulling out all the stops to boost
OL,16,Fproductivity while delivering tough
OL,17,Fefficiency measures".
