OL,6,FShe added: "It's vital we take
OL,7,Fdecisive action to tackle the deep-
OL,8,Frooted causes of pressures on the
OL,9,Fhealth services including the lack of
OL,10,Fresources for public health,
OL,11,Fprevention and social care, chronic
OL,12,Fworkforce shortages, financial
OL,13,Fshortfalls and historic under-
OL,14,Finvestment in the bricks and mortar of
OL,15,Fthe NHS which underpin so many of the
OL,16,Fchallenges we face today.
