OL,6,FNuffield Trust's chief executive
OL,7,Fexpressed concerns about what the
OL,8,Fleague tables will measure: "A table
OL,9,Fbased on general waiting times doesn't
OL,10,Fadd much if you need to know how good
OL,11,Fheart surgery is.
OL,13,F"Many of the drivers of poor
OL,14,Fproductivity are systemic, from the
OL,15,Fdire state of social care stranding
OL,16,Fpeople in hospital, to crumbling roofs
OL,17,Fand worsening population health.
