OL,6,F"They happen across England. Which
OL,7,Ftrust is worst affected is often a
OL,8,Fmatter of luck and history as much as
OL,9,Fleadership.
OL,11,F"We need a system that encourages
OL,12,Fleaders to go to the most difficult
OL,13,Fand challenged trusts to improve
OL,14,Fpatient care, not one that rewards
OL,15,Fthem for choosing easier places to
OL,16,Fwork." said Thea Stein.
