OL,6,FStreeting will also tell Wednesday's
OL,7,Fconference how NHS trusts could be
OL,8,Fbanned from using agencies to cover
OL,9,Fstaffing gaps such as healthcare
OL,10,Fassistants and cleaners, in a bid to
OL,11,Fcut the #3 billion a year spent on
OL,12,Fagency workers.
OL,14,FThose NHS staff who leave permanent
OL,15,Fjobs could also be stopped from coming
OL,16,Fback into the health service through
OL,17,Fexpensive agencies.
